{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 1968, "height": 2719, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "谱例", "block_bbox": [814, 227, 1022, 291], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "一、杜氏明代宗谱久佚，清乾隆年间复创修谱志，民国7年（1981）一续，1963年二续，1988年三续，旧谱除序言外，仅是简单的世系排谱。本谱为2008年四续本，2010年付梓。虽是续编，而多所新创，意在建立当代新型家谱。", "block_bbox": [183, 358, 1640, 535], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "二、旧定家谱为三十年一续，现在时代发展日新月异，兹定续修间隔为二十年。", "block_bbox": [270, 552, 1625, 602], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三、本谱卷首，刊像赞图照，次以谱序、谱例、修谱人名、捐资额等。", "block_bbox": [273, 619, 1398, 668], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "四、卷首而外，正文有史略篇、世系表、人物篇、文化篇等四部分。末殿以附录。", "block_bbox": [273, 685, 1629, 733], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "五、世系表为宗谱之主体。编谱一遵欧体，五世一表，以欧体“合收而易考”，亲疏昭穆，条贯井然，从上而下直书则见祖孙之传承，从右而左横书则见昆季之同辈。", "block_bbox": [186, 751, 1643, 864], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "六、为彰显本支始祖，明晰本支传承迁徙地，特于整个世系表前加塔式世系图谱，并在每支世系表前加以文字说明。\n", "block_bbox": [186, 880, 1641, 990], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "七、人谱成员不分性别，均标以生卒年。嗣子后，标出配偶姓名、生卒年及子女数。桃女后，标出赘婿姓名、生卒年及子女数。继子，不分本姓、他姓，如嗣子标法。出嫁女，标适地及婿姓名。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 1008, 1643, 1185], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "八、迁徙者，在其名后详标迁居地，以为后之有考。", "block_bbox": [270, 1204, 1133, 1250], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "九、迁徙至洛宁县城一支，又分迁至洛宁营里村，后分下营、杨坡西官庄、东官庄及渑池下庄沟（杜家阙)，旧未入总谱，兹次访查增入。惟杨坡西官庄、东官庄二处仍缺，待后补续。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 1268, 1644, 1443], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十、旧谱原有孟村门，一居城关郑窑，一居孟村，且所出不同，经本门代表和与修谱委员会商定，析为城关郑窑和孟村两支。\n", "block_bbox": [185, 1463, 1643, 1573], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十一、杜姓人物，首列全国历代名人，次记本支古今有发展、有贡献者。", "block_bbox": [271, 1593, 1487, 1639], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十二、杜氏文化分两部分。中国杜氏记：杜姓家谱、郡望堂号、杜氏楹联、家训格言等；渑池杜氏记：传说故事、杜氏家训、杜氏宗祠、碑刻辑录、县志有关记述等。", "block_bbox": [187, 1657, 1644, 1767], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十三、附录列尧帝事略、洪洞寻根、杜姓书籍、姓氏排序及中国的谱牒祠堂等。", "block_bbox": [270, 1786, 1606, 1833], "block_id": 13, "block_order": 14}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十四、每年清明节，举行祭祖仪式，各支各村应选代表参加为是。一为尊祖敬宗，不忘其本；二为增进族谊，共谋发展。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 1850, 1645, 1962], "block_id": 14, "block_order": 15}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "十五、宗谱字号，乃为后之确认世次而定，且防止单名和重名。仍旧谱字号照列，以便据之起名。自十六世到三十世依次为：宗、信、克、太、平，国、正、天、心、顺，官、清、民、自、安。\n", "block_bbox": [184, 1981, 1643, 2162], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 16}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9359540343284607, "coordinate": [184.1064453125, 1981.490478515625, 1643.958251953125, 2162.803955078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9329309463500977, "coordinate": [185.76019287109375, 1268.4278564453125, 1644.060791015625, 1443.7569580078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9176403284072876, "coordinate": [183.62225341796875, 358.921142578125, 1640.606689453125, 535.339599609375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9170111417770386, "coordinate": [185.73931884765625, 1008.891845703125, 1643.509521484375, 1185.0498046875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.906898021697998, "coordinate": [185.87615966796875, 1463.4619140625, 1643.62890625, 1573.01416015625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9022705554962158, "coordinate": [184.02569580078125, 1850.8289794921875, 1645.60595703125, 1962.8133544921875]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9017049670219421, "coordinate": [187.32745361328125, 1657.8759765625, 1644.094970703125, 1767.89990234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8843902945518494, "coordinate": [186.71051025390625, 880.5067749023438, 1641.793212890625, 990.0596313476562]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8501545190811157, "coordinate": [186.92376708984375, 751.2335815429688, 1643.366455078125, 864.1035766601562]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8468088507652283, "coordinate": [271.4190673828125, 1593.1990966796875, 1487.7393798828125, 1639.8255615234375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8300860524177551, "coordinate": [270.78082275390625, 1204.471923828125, 1133.778564453125, 1250.292236328125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.8165575265884399, "coordinate": [270.20263671875, 1786.841064453125, 1606.36962890625, 1833.51708984375]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7366639375686646, "coordinate": [273.24267578125, 685.235595703125, 1629.66455078125, 733.737548828125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7341117262840271, "coordinate": [273.09552001953125, 619.8394775390625, 1398.8125, 668.2916259765625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.7230499982833862, "coordinate": [270.3521728515625, 552.475341796875, 1625.5975341796875, 602.5701904296875]}, {"cls_id": 0, "label": "paragraph_title", "score": 0.6928936839103699, "coordinate": [814.0499877929688, 227.0709228515625, 1022.0967407226562, 291.13812255859375]}]}, "overall_ocr_res": {"model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_textline_orientation": true}, "dt_polys": [[[814, 223], [1028, 223], [1028, 299], [814, 299]], [[276, 359], [1638, 359], [1638, 406], [276, 406]], [[193, 425], [1635, 425], [1635, 469], [193, 469]], [[191, 488],